{"tid":625231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子眀愛向晴軒內上吊亡","createTime":"2018-04-11T09:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T03:55:16.000Z","uid":41404,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7cdc606d4df799a84dd9d1b0a461c0590fb942","tid":625231,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"【16:45更新】警方調查後，相信男事主因家庭及金錢問題不開心尋死<br />\n<br />\n牛頭角觀塘道50號明愛向晴軒，中午1時40分，一名中年男子被職員發現在中心內上吊，救護員到場時男事主已陷入昏迷，送醫院搶救後不治。<br />\n現場消息指，男死者被發現走出一樓圍欄上吊。警員調查證實死者為66歲姓張男子，在場沒有撿獲遺書，相信他因家庭及金錢問題不開心尋死，案件無可疑。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n<strong>明愛向晴熱線：18288</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180411/58059687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58059687&d=9Q56bAYsZhWDnGmmLrhNDi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=19e0eff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58059687&h=81052a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180411/58059687</a>"},{"pid":"ae15f844d698e0154bbc0ac69ca288100e92f5d1","tid":625231,"uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"愁爆男想搵人幫又變卦　向晴軒平台笨豬跳式吊頸亡<br />\n<br />\n九龍灣觀塘道50號向晴軒，下午1時許，2名職員發現一名姓張(66歲)男子，在一樓平台用繩綁圍欄「笨豬跳」式吊頸，身體懸在半空。消防接報到場將張解下，惟他已奄奄一息，由救護車送院，搶救後不治。據悉，死者是到向晴軒求助時輕生。 <br />\n<br />\n警方在場未檢獲遺書，初步調查相信張因家庭及金錢問題不開心尋死，案件無可疑，通知其家人到醫院。 <br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒網頁介紹，該機構為正面對危機的人士提供一站式服務，協助受助者以正面態度去解決個人及家庭危機，並推動他們繼續接受適切的專業輔導及支援服務。服務形式包括提供24小時運作之「向晴熱線」、短暫住宿服務、危機介入及評估、輔導服務、治療及互助小組及社區教育活動等。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n<strong>明愛向晴軒： 18288 </strong><br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411150335629-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180411150335629-0411_00822_001.html&d=9Q56bAYsZhWDnGmmLrhNDi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=002abff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411150335629-0411_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e26578e17815ad6418bae8922a7a3103aba34995","tid":625231,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0102bd0740e742fbc6b56a9bfadc548c27f664cc","tid":625231,"uid":11598,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係諷刺"},{"pid":"f2cb1fca9fcfa2381a6933a0ff358f1df54aa0c8","tid":625231,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"Oh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9fddc41c507eef5ddd4db2b201d03af2d5d275","tid":625231,"uid":159163,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 明愛向晴軒： 18288 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c9aaebf1555cb928eed686bda8d24e0301328dd8","tid":625231,"uid":10844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"打去然後自己接聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68451582151b58a07dfd7e2f0f4998258e001a0a","tid":625231,"uid":55990,"like":1,"dislike":0